<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Den2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Den,</orth> abbreviation for <emph>evening</emph> or <emph>even</emph> in <cit><quote>Good den:</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 3.2.83" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado III, 2, 83</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ado 5.1.46" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 46</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jn 1.185" default="NO" valid="yes">John I, 185</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.1.41" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 1, 41</bibl>. cf. <emph>Godgigoden</emph> and <emph>Good-den.</emph>
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>